title: Frontend Developer
description: We are looking for a talented Frontend Developer to join our team
requirements: At least 2 years of experience with React

title: Backend Developer
description: Join our backend team to build scalable server-side applications using Node.js and Express. You will work on designing APIs, database architecture, and ensuring system performance.
requirements: 3+ years experience with Node.js, Express, MongoDB. Strong understanding of RESTful APIs and microservices architecture.

title: Full Stack Developer
description: We're seeking a versatile Full Stack Developer to work on both frontend and backend development. You'll be responsible for creating complete web applications from conception to deployment.
requirements: 4+ years of experience with React, Node.js, and database technologies. Experience with cloud platforms is a plus.

title: Data Scientist
description: Join our AI team to develop machine learning models and analyze large datasets. You'll work on predictive analytics and data-driven solutions for our clients.
requirements: Master's degree in Data Science or related field. 3+ years experience with Python, TensorFlow, and statistical analysis.

title: DevOps Engineer
description: We need a DevOps Engineer to manage our cloud infrastructure and CI/CD pipelines. You'll ensure scalability, reliability, and security of our applications.
requirements: 3+ years with AWS/Azure, Docker, Kubernetes, Jenkins. Experience with infrastructure as code and monitoring tools.
